# zsh hooks, array of functions
$chpwd_functions
functions inside this array are called Hook Functions

## zsh functionalities
1. trap functions

# Special functions in ZSH => Hook Functions
add-zsh-hook
[7] hook is one of chpwd, periodic, precmd, preexec, zshaddhistory, zshexit, or zsh_directory_name

# autoloading functions
functions can be marked as undefined, lazy-load using builtins like: autoload, functions -u, typeset -fu
such functions has NO BODY, shell searches for its definition using fpath vairable
